    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DbxRuntimeException.AccessDenied, DbxRuntimeException.BadState, DbxRuntimeException.BadType, DbxRuntimeException.Cache, DbxRuntimeException.IllegalArgument, DbxRuntimeException.Internal, DbxRuntimeException.Memory, DbxRuntimeException.NotCached, DbxRuntimeException.SizeLimit, DbxRuntimeException.System

    public class DbxRuntimeException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException
implements DbxThrowable
    Base class for unchecked exceptions in the SDK. Inner subtypes distinguish types of Exceptions so your app can respond appropriately, but the base class can be used as a catch-all.
